#: ../../language/error_codes/E4201.md:1
msgid "E4201"
msgstr "E4201"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4201.md:3
msgid "Compiler diagnostic name: `struct_constr_inconsistent_impl`."
msgstr "编译器诊断名称：`struct_constr_inconsistent_impl`。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4201.md:5
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The implementation of a legacy in-struct constructor signature must have "
"the same parameter and return types as the declaration in the `struct`. A"
" function with a different signature is not an implementation of that "
"constructor."
msgstr "结构体构造器的实现必须与 `struct` 中的构造器声明具有相同的参数类型和返回类型。签名不同的方法不是该构造器的实现。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4201.md:9
msgid "Erroneous example"
msgstr "错误示例"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4201.md:11
msgid ""
"///|\n"
"priv struct Point {\n"
"  x : Int\n"
"\n"
"  fn new(Int) -> Point\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"///|\n"
"fn Point::new(text : String) -> Point {\n"
"  { x: text.length() }\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4201.md:15
msgid "Suggestion"
msgstr "建议"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4201.md:17
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Change either the constructor declaration or the `Type::Type` "
"implementation so their signatures match."
msgstr "修改构造器声明或 `Type::new` 实现，使两者的签名保持一致。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4201.md:20
msgid ""
"///|\n"
"priv struct Point {\n"
"  x : Int\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"///|\n"
"fn Point::Point(x : Int) -> Point {\n"
"  { x, }\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"///|\n"
"test {\n"
"  let point = Point(2)\n"
"  inspect(point.x, content=\"2\")\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""

